Former Louis Trichardt resident and musician Jacques Mouton has entered for the Smashing Productions Lockdown Challenge. He invited people to “Like” his video on Facebook. This is his message: "Hey awesome people! This is my entry for the smashing lockdown challenge! Thought it would be fitting for the times we are in. Please go and LIKE my video (Click here) directly on Smashing Promotions for the vote to count. The video with the most likes on their page will be the winner. Thanks for all your love and support!"